summary: PepsiCo joins the growing list of advertisers pouring millions into Formula 1’s global audience.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell HPQ and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Shareholders of HP would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 25.6% and now trades at $24.15. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
